TTS-Flite version 0.02
======================

use TTS::Flite;
my $tts = TTS::Flite->new();

$tts->init();  # call it only once, before calling tts().
$tts->tts("Some String");

INSTALLATION

On debian(10+) and ubuntu(18.04+) systems

    sudo apt install libflite1

    git clone https://github.com/rkrt/TTS-Flite
    cd TTS-Flite
    sudo cpan install .

